<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 18:09:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列侨民部长在马德里 Vox 会议上赞扬西班牙极右翼“与以色列结盟”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-minister-praises-spains-far-right-vox-for-aligning-with-israel/0000018f-91bd-d212-abcf-d7fdfe550000</link><description>以色列的阿米猜·奇克利与极右翼同行玛丽娜·勒庞、乔治亚·梅洛尼、维克多·欧尔班、哈维尔·米莱和 Vox 的圣地亚哥·阿巴斯卡尔一起宣称，加沙战争“是一场针对西方文明的未来、反对激进伊斯兰的生死存亡之战”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 17:37:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-minister-praises-spains-far-right-vox-for-aligning-with-israel/0000018f-91bd-d212-abcf-d7fdfe550000</guid></item><item><title>“亲以色列”阴谋论者埃莉斯·斯特凡尼克来到以色列向特朗普求婚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-19/ty-article/.highlight/pro-israel-conspiracy-theorist-elise-stefanik-came-to-israel-to-court-trump/0000018f-91c4-d9a7-a9af-dbcef8a20000</link><description>与斯特凡尼克一样，绝大多数作为特朗普竞选搭档的潜在候选人公开出现的名字都倾向于全力支持以色列战争，同时攻击巴勒斯坦人和他们的支持者</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 17:30:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-19/ty-article/.highlight/pro-israel-conspiracy-theorist-elise-stefanik-came-to-israel-to-court-trump/0000018f-91c4-d9a7-a9af-dbcef8a20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和巴勒斯坦和平活动人士会见教皇，分享他们对共同未来的梦想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-palestinian-peace-activists-meet-pope-to-share-their-dream-of-a-shared-future/0000018f-9186-d212-abcf-d7efcfe30000</link><description>毛兹·伊农 (Maoz Inon) 的父母于 10 月 7 日被杀，阿齐兹·阿布·萨拉 (Aziz Abu Sarah) 在第二次起义中失去了弟弟，他们在 13,000 名群众面前向教皇方济各发表讲话。教皇表示，他们的工作“不仅证明了对和平的渴望，而且是面向未来的计划”</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 16:47:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-palestinian-peace-activists-meet-pope-to-share-their-dream-of-a-shared-future/0000018f-9186-d212-abcf-d7efcfe30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 226 天：以色列国防军命令加沙北部拜特拉希亚居民撤离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-226-idf-orders-residents-in-north-gazas-beit-lahia-to-evacuate/0000018f-91b1-d9d1-abcf-d7fdbd860000</link><description>美国国家安全顾问沙利文正在以色列会见总理内塔尼亚胡和战时内阁部长甘茨 ■ 极右翼部长斯莫特里奇呼吁，如果真主党拒绝从边境撤军，以色列就占领加沙并入侵黎巴嫩南部 ■ 约旦外交部长呼吁调查此事他声称这是以色列在加沙战役期间犯下的战争罪 ■ 这是战争进入 226 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 16:35:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-226-idf-orders-residents-in-north-gazas-beit-lahia-to-evacuate/0000018f-91b1-d9d1-abcf-d7fdbd860000</guid></item><item><title>在取消和强烈抗议后，以色列耶路撒冷四重奏在阿姆斯特丹举行音乐会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/after-anti-israel-call-for-cancellation-jerusalem-quartet-plays-amsterdam-concert/0000018f-9110-d212-abcf-d77d8d9a0000</link><description>包括顶尖音乐家在内的超过 13,000 人签署了一份请愿书，呼吁阿姆斯特丹音乐厅允许耶路撒冷四重奏乐团进行演出，周六它也这样做了。音乐会和场外小型亲巴勒斯坦抗议活动顺利通过</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 15:56:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/after-anti-israel-call-for-cancellation-jerusalem-quartet-plays-amsterdam-concert/0000018f-9110-d212-abcf-d77d8d9a0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦消息人士明确表示，以色列支持的当地实体无法管理加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-sources-are-making-it-clear-that-no-israel-backed-local-entity-can-govern-gaza/0000018f-914b-d17a-a9df-915b5e5f0000</link><description>加沙的一位知名人士告诉《国土报》，“任何敢于执行这项任务的人都将是一名承包商，往好里说是无法承受压力，往坏了说是无法承受以色列的庇护”。然而，一项关于建立多国部队和外交进程的提议正在获得更多支持</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 15:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-sources-are-making-it-clear-that-no-israel-backed-local-entity-can-govern-gaza/0000018f-914b-d17a-a9df-915b5e5f0000</guid></item><item><title>按照这个速度，以色列活不过100岁生日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-this-rate-israel-wont-make-it-to-its-100th-birthday/0000018f-90cf-d065-a7ef-baff65310000</link><description>政府行政专家尤金·坎德尔和罗恩·祖尔在一篇新论文中警告说，一旦以色列精英看到各个“部落”无法就社会契约达成一致，他们就会逃离该国</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 14:15:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-this-rate-israel-wont-make-it-to-its-100th-birthday/0000018f-90cf-d065-a7ef-baff65310000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长斯莫特里奇呼吁占领加沙并接管黎巴嫩南部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-far-right-minister-smotrich-calls-to-occupy-gaza-take-over-south-lebanon/0000018f-90d7-d926-a18f-f5d7564d0000</link><description>贝扎莱·斯莫特里奇表示，只有在加沙地带永久存在才能阻止以色列南部的火箭弹。他说，应该向真主党发出最后通牒——从边境撤军，否则将面临以色列的入侵</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 12:42:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-far-right-minister-smotrich-calls-to-occupy-gaza-take-over-south-lebanon/0000018f-90d7-d926-a18f-f5d7564d0000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列士兵在加沙南部丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-southern-gaza/0000018f-90a8-d9a7-a9af-dbaec6520000</link><description>两名阵亡士兵被确认为 20 岁的纳赫曼·梅尔·海姆·瓦克宁中士和 20 岁的诺姆·比坦中士。第三名士兵加尔·沙巴特少校因上周在加沙战斗中受伤而死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 11:56:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-southern-gaza/0000018f-90a8-d9a7-a9af-dbaec6520000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日失去家人的以色列人遭到右翼抗议者袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-who-lost-his-family-on-october-7-assaulted-by-right-wing-protesters/0000018f-9074-d17a-a9df-9175244e0000</link><description>加迪·凯德姆 (Gadi Kedem) 在哈马斯袭击中失去了女儿、女婿和孙子，他向警方报案；本-格维尔部长称凯德姆是施暴者</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 11:15:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-who-lost-his-family-on-october-7-assaulted-by-right-wing-protesters/0000018f-9074-d17a-a9df-9175244e0000</guid></item><item><title>这位贝都因-以色列网球教练希望为她的社区实现更大的目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-05-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-bedouin-israeli-tennis-coach-wants-to-serve-a-bigger-purpose-for-her-community/0000018f-7c83-dd4f-ab8f-fdaf6a8f0000</link><description>26 岁的舒鲁克·斯瓦德·塞勒姆 (Shuruq Swaed Salem) 从未打过网球。 30 岁之前，她是一家独特的体育中心的副主任，该中心汇集了所有宗教信仰的以色列儿童</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 09:43:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-05-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-bedouin-israeli-tennis-coach-wants-to-serve-a-bigger-purpose-for-her-community/0000018f-7c83-dd4f-ab8f-fdaf6a8f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙战斗中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article-live/idf-deploys-another-brigade-in-rafah-estimates-800-000-palestinians-left-the-city/0000018f-8ed6-d9a7-a9af-dfde36650000</link><description>数十名以色列人在约旦河西岸投掷石块并破坏巴勒斯坦卡车；两人被捕 ■ 以色列国防军：以色列军队在加沙杀害了一名哈马斯高级官员 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，加沙有 35,456 名巴勒斯坦人被杀，79,476 人受伤 ■ 财政部长斯莫特里奇：如果真主党不响应最后通牒，以色列必须接管黎巴嫩南部 ■ 共和党众议员斯特凡尼克在以色列议会发表讲话，谴责拜登政府“阻止对以色列的援助”</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 03:35:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article-live/idf-deploys-another-brigade-in-rafah-estimates-800-000-palestinians-left-the-city/0000018f-8ed6-d9a7-a9af-dfde36650000</guid></item><item><title>人质尸体的打捞使公众重新关注被关押在加沙的以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/recovery-of-hostages-bodies-places-public-focus-back-on-israelis-held-in-gaza/0000018f-8d58-d17a-a9df-9d59e7730000</link><description>在过去两周从头条新闻中消失后，关于打捞和辨认四名以色列人质尸体的公告使人质的困境重新回到了公众议程中的适当位置。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 03:09:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/recovery-of-hostages-bodies-places-public-focus-back-on-israelis-held-in-gaza/0000018f-8d58-d17a-a9df-9d59e7730000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡还能抵御提前选举和加沙战略吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/can-netanyahu-still-fend-off-early-elections-and-a-strategy-for-gaza/0000018f-8d4b-d926-a18f-edcf2da80000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的战时内阁伙伴约夫·加兰特和本尼·甘茨现在都对他投了不信任票。但甘茨发表了相当懦弱的演讲，总理根本没有兴趣解雇他</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 20:06:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/can-netanyahu-still-fend-off-early-elections-and-a-strategy-for-gaza/0000018f-8d4b-d926-a18f-edcf2da80000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨要求在6月8日之前制定战后加沙计划，否则他将辞去内塔尼亚胡政府职务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/gantz-demands-post-war-gaza-plan-by-june-8-or-he-will-quit-netanyahu-govt/0000018f-8d03-ded1-a7df-dd5319040000</link><description>战时内阁部长在新闻发布会上表示，“个人和政治考虑已进入以色列国防最神圣的部分”，并呼吁内塔尼亚胡总理“做正确的事”</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 19:41:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/gantz-demands-post-war-gaza-plan-by-june-8-or-he-will-quit-netanyahu-govt/0000018f-8d03-ded1-a7df-dd5319040000</guid></item><item><title>人质罗恩·本亚明的尸体从加沙地带运回以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/body-of-hostage-ron-binyamin-retrieved-to-israel-from-gaza/0000018f-8ca0-d9d6-a38f-8dfb43e10000</link><description>以色列军方宣布，53 岁的本亚明的尸体于周五与人质沙尼·洛克、阿米特·布斯基拉和伊扎克·格勒伦特一起被打捞上岸。他是两个孩子的父亲，自 10 月 7 日以来命运未卜。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 17:37:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/body-of-hostage-ron-binyamin-retrieved-to-israel-from-gaza/0000018f-8ca0-d9d6-a38f-8dfb43e10000</guid></item><item><title>当无人谈论时，她领导了争取妇女和 LGBTQ 权利的斗争：Yael Dayan 是一位泰坦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/she-fought-for-womens-and-lgbtq-rights-when-no-one-else-was-yael-dayan-was-a-titan/0000018f-8c91-d7a5-abcf-8dbb32a70000</link><description>即使在生病之后，达扬仍然是一位忠实的公众人物，她可怕的疾病成为她处理的另一个问题。她无所畏惧，抚养了一代年轻人，他们将在这里建立一个模范社会</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 17:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/she-fought-for-womens-and-lgbtq-rights-when-no-one-else-was-yael-dayan-was-a-titan/0000018f-8c91-d7a5-abcf-8dbb32a70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第225天：外国消息人士称，停战谈判陷入“僵局”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-225-truce-talks-are-at-an-impasse-foreign-source-says/0000018f-8c7e-d9d6-a38f-8dffd6100000</link><description>一位熟悉谈判的外国消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列和哈马斯之间的停战谈判“没有取得任何进展”。 ■ 白宫表示，以色列愿意在就拉法的广泛军事行动做出重大决定之前继续进行谈判。组建“人道主义卫队”，保护援助车队免受以色列极右活动分子的袭击 ■ 战争进入 225 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 16:40:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-225-truce-talks-are-at-an-impasse-foreign-source-says/0000018f-8c7e-d9d6-a38f-8dffd6100000</guid></item><item><title>反对党领袖拉皮德呼吁甘茨和艾森科特离开政府，以色列各地数千人举行抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/hostage-release-and-anti-government-protests-to-be-held-across-israel-on-saturday-night/0000018f-8c17-d273-a1af-aed7e2800000</link><description>数十名反政府抗议者封锁了特拉维夫的阿亚隆高速公路，美国大使在特拉维夫的人质集会上发表讲话。周一，在议会夏季会议开幕之前，抗议车队前往耶路撒冷</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 15:33:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/hostage-release-and-anti-government-protests-to-be-held-across-israel-on-saturday-night/0000018f-8c17-d273-a1af-aed7e2800000</guid></item><item><title>定居者袭击了他们认为正在向加沙运送援助物资的巴勒斯坦卡车司机以及前来治疗他的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/settlers-attack-trucker-thought-to-be-delivering-aid-to-gaza-and-soldiers-who-helped-him/0000018f-8687-d443-adef-9fcf68460000</link><description>在最近一次定居者反对向加沙运送人道主义援助的暴力抗议中，一辆卡车被迫停在科恰夫·哈沙哈尔定居点附近并被焚烧，导致司机中度受伤，三名前来援助他的以色列国防军士兵受轻伤。没有逮捕任何人</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 14:35:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/settlers-attack-trucker-thought-to-be-delivering-aid-to-gaza-and-soldiers-who-helped-him/0000018f-8687-d443-adef-9fcf68460000</guid></item></channel></rss>